injury.description: Aug 17: Bernard-Converse is doubtful to return to Saturday's preseason matchup against the Panthers due to a groin injury, Brian Costello of the New York Post reports.
Aug 19: Carter (ankle) is considered day-to-day and is expected to be re-evaluated at the end of the week, Rich Cimini of ESPN.com reports.
Aug 24: Newman has been ruled out for the rest of Saturday's game against the Giants due to a shoulder injury, Zack Rosenblatt of The Athletic reports.
Aug 17: Charles is questionable to return to Saturday's exhibition contest against Carolina due to a hip injury.
Aug 6: Smith (undisclosed) was not on the field for team drills at training camp Tuesday, Andy Vasquez of The Bergen Record reports.
Aug 24: Mitchell is questionable to return to Saturday's preseason game against the Giants after sustaining a shoulder injury, Brian Costello of the New York Post reports.
Aug 29: Coach Robert Saleh said Thursday that Williams (knee) is expected to be available for New York's regular-season opener against the 49ers on Monday, Sept. 9, Rich Cimini of ESPN.com reports.
Aug 15: Williams missed practice Thursday with a shoulder injury, Rich Cimini of ESPN.com reports.
Aug 29: Reddick still has not reported to the Jets' facility as of Thursday, but general manager Joe Douglas has no plans to trade him, Zack Rosenblatt of The Athletic reports.
